{"tid":2371782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西准用科興疫苗 總統拒接種","createTime":"2021-01-19T06:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T06:46:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bca55ea1c42c0b4561647b8298f0eaefe660891","tid":2371782,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210119/J3YQ24FOPFCKFHNF3IIYDD6P6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210119%2FJ3YQ24FOPFCKFHNF3IIYDD6P6U%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=049ea635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210119%2FJ3YQ24FOPFCKFHNF3IIYDD6P6U%2F&h=75083f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210119/J3YQ24FOPFCKFHNF3IIYDD6P6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n巴西准用科興疫苗 總統拒接種<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MQ5QYZAzcFbjeg89Ic_FtNdRpx0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOQY6BYSQZGOLJ67KW5DMNANVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMQ5QYZAzcFbjeg89Ic_FtNdRpx0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOQY6BYSQZGOLJ67KW5DMNANVM.jpg&h=ed51300f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巴西聖保羅一間醫院的醫護人員，前日接種當地首批科興疫苗。路透社<br />\n<br />\n巴西武漢肺炎疫情嚴峻，國家衞生監測局前日批准緊急使用兩款疫苗，包括由英國牛津大學與阿斯利康藥廠共同研發的疫苗，另一款是巴西早前公佈、整體有效率只有50.38％的中國科興CoronaVac疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n當局批准緊急使用疫苗後，聖保羅市54歲深切治療部護士卡拉贊斯率先接種科興CoronaVac疫苗，是巴西首位接種者，。。。。。。。。。。。。。雖然曾染疫的總統博爾索納羅表明不會打針，並質疑中國製疫苗，但民眾仍期待接種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國擴大接種範圍<br />\n<br />\n疫情同樣嚴峻的英國亦加緊為民眾接種疫苗，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／路透社"},{"pid":"8487a8f622a7fc2e4d9404acf01dfcbdd2baa2a5","tid":2371782,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"讓人民先來"},{"pid":"ee3511ffdef220cc8c57c91bc990663bff66d379","tid":2371782,"uid":138713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8487a8f622a7fc2e4d9404acf01dfcbdd2baa2a5","tid":2371782,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"讓人民先來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"讓人民先來(當白老鼠)"},{"pid":"f018c2a37c086b6fb62c4891d2c5f4ae9438a36e","tid":2371782,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"巴西總統一向都話冇事 應該唔關係咪科興事 同埋佢都中過 應該有免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe0b63e50632eb3ef46eebc7b169ee73ae8de84","tid":2371782,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abd143a9049d4c61ba293e3167d6320bc364630","tid":2371782,"uid":44349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee3511ffdef220cc8c57c91bc990663bff66d379","tid":2371782,"uid":138713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8487a8f622a7fc2e4d9404acf01dfcbdd2baa2a5","tid":2371782,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:29:46.000Z","msg":"讓人民先來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"讓人民先來(當白老鼠)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"好似係總統一直反對引入科興疫苗<br />\n但係衞生局批准"},{"pid":"fcbfdcd8e558ae635ca30bb7534de4206ec9a78a","tid":2371782,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f018c2a37c086b6fb62c4891d2c5f4ae9438a36e","tid":2371782,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"巴西總統一向都話冇事 應該唔關係咪科興事 同埋佢都中過 應該有免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T06:35:39.000Z"